# ::snt-1 A group of kids is playing in a yard and an old man is standing in the background
(z1 / and
      :op1 (z2 / play-01
            :ARG0 (z3 / group
                  :consist-of (z4 / kid))
            :location (z5 / yard))
      :op2 (z6 / stand-01
            :ARG1 (z7 / man
                  :mod (z8 / old))
            :ARG2 (z9 / background)))

# ::snt-2 A group of children is playing in the house and there is no man standing in the background

            :location (z5 / house))
      :op2 (z6 / stand-01

            :ARG1 (z7 / man)
            :ARG2 (z8 / background)))
